
---- How to use the Account Class ----


login("username") -- 1 Argument: String username of player
	Returns Account Object
	*Must be called whenever a player logs in

getId() -- does not take any arguments
	Returns Integer value of player id

getUsername() -- does not take any arguments
	Returns String value of player username

getRealname() -- does not take any arguments
	Returns String value of player real name
	*Format of return: "[firstname] [lastname]"

getGamesWon() -- does not take any arguments
	Returns Integer value of player's number of games won

getGamesPlayed() -- does not take any arguments
	Returns Integer value of player's number of games played

getScore() -- does not take any arguments
	Returns Integer value of player's score

gameStart(account) -- 1 Argument: Account object of opponent
	Returns nothing 
	[sets an instance variable used for later calculations]
	*Must be called before a game begins

gameWon() -- does not take any arguments
	Returns nothing
	[updates player score, games_played value, and games_won value]

gameTied() -- does not take any arguments
	Returns nothing
	[updates player score and games_played value]

gameLost() -- does not take any arguments
	Returns nothing
	[updates player score and games_played value]

getFriendsList() -- does not take any arguments
	Returns an Array of Friend Objects

removeFriend(friend) -- 1 Argument: Username of friend to remove from friends list
	Returns nothing

requestFriend(player) -- 1 Argument: Username of player to request friendship of
	Returns nothing

acceptFriend(player) -- 1 Argument: Username of player to accept friend request from
	Returns nothing

denyFriend(player) -- 1 Argument: Username of player to deny friend request from
	Returns nothing

getAccountsOnline() -- does not take any arguments
	Returns Integer value of the number of players online

logout() -- does not take any arguments
	Returns nothing
	[updates database from Account object values]



---- How to use the Friend Class ----


getUsername() -- does not take any arguments
	Returns String value of Friend's username

getRealname() -- does not take any arguments
	Returns String value of Friend's real name
	*Format of return: "[firstname] [lastname]"

getScore() -- does not take any arguments
	Returns Integer value of Friend's score

getOnline() -- does not take any arguments
	Returns Boolean value of Friend's online status
	*true if Friend is online, false otherwise


